<title>GERMANY: UBS - 26.1 pct of Adidas share capital placed.</title>
<headline>UBS - 26.1 pct of Adidas share capital placed.</headline>
<dateline>FRANKFURT 1997-04-11</dateline>
<text>
<p>UBS Limited, global coordinator and bookrunner for the sale of Sogedim S.A's stake in German sportswear maker Adidas AG said on Friday that 26.1 percent of Adidas' total share capital had been successfully placed at 181 marks.</p>
<p>Adidas CEO Robert Louis-Dreyfus, and Christian Tourres, member of the Adidas management board, have each purchased 2.95 million shares through the offering, each representing a 6.5 percent share of Adidas share capital, UBS said.</p>
<p>Adidas announced on Thursday that Sogedim would put its stake up for sale.</p>
<p>--Frankfurt Newsroom +49 69 756525</p>
